<doc id="1207955" wikidata="Q227373" url="?curid=1207955" title="War (disambiguation)">
<text>A [[War]] is a large-scale armed conflict and the term is used as a metaphor for non-military conflicts.

War or WAR may also refer to:

==Places==
* War, West Virginia
* War Creek, a stream in West Virginia
* Warwickshire county in England, standard code

==Music==

===Performers===
* War (band), an American 1970s funk band

